Uh, by the way,                 
Lionel,                         

13:09.855 --> 13:11.555
    as long as you're here,     
        do you remember         

13:11.557 --> 13:13.957
that little brunette            
girlfriend of Gloria's?         

13:13.959 --> 13:16.026
Her name                        
was Trudy, Trudy...             

13:16.028 --> 13:17.127
            Uh, Trudy Brightman.

13:17.129 --> 13:18.962
Brightman.                      
Brightman, yeah.                

13:18.964 --> 13:20.464
See you around, Lionel.         

13:20.466 --> 13:21.666
            What about Trudy?   

13:21.668 --> 13:25.303
Oh, uh, I don't know.           
I ain't heard nothing.          

13:26.605 --> 13:28.138
             You want me to tell
                Mike anything?  

13:28.140 --> 13:31.875
Yeah. Tell him to send us       
a card, Christmas and Easter.   

13:35.079 --> 13:38.382
Brightman, Brightman, Brightman.

13:38.384 --> 13:41.919
          That was "B"          
     when I went to school.     

13:41.921 --> 13:43.621
        Let's see.              

13:43.623 --> 13:46.757
Brightman and, uh, "B"...       

13:46.759 --> 13:49.593
    and it ain't here.          

13:49.595 --> 13:53.063
    Where would Edith write     
        that name?              

13:53.065 --> 13:56.867
     Oh, yeah, yeah, yeah.      

13:56.869 --> 13:58.068
        Let's see here.         

13:58.070 --> 14:00.805
     Here it is. Brightman.     

