    ♪ If you're happy           
 And you know it, say "I am" ♪  

14:20.926 --> 14:21.959
          ♪ I am! ♪             

14:21.961 --> 14:22.960
That was good, Ma.              

14:22.962 --> 14:24.395
                  Mrs. Bunker,  
                you're terrific.

14:24.397 --> 14:25.929
     Oh, my, that was fun.      

14:25.931 --> 14:29.700
      I just love singing,      
    especially songs.           

14:32.303 --> 14:33.937
                  Oh, more wine,
                Mrs. Bunker?    

14:33.939 --> 14:36.340
Oh, my, it is empty again.      

14:36.342 --> 14:38.108
Thank you.                      

14:39.378 --> 14:40.611
Ma!                             

14:42.914 --> 14:44.682
        You know,               
    this is just like           

14:44.684 --> 14:48.552
sitting around a campfire       
            at camp,            

14:48.554 --> 14:50.421
      only we ain't itchy.      

14:50.423 --> 14:51.955
        [LAUGHTER]              

14:54.860 --> 14:59.430
        Oh, I used              
to love them song-alings.       

14:59.432 --> 15:01.665
Sing-alongs, Ma.                

15:01.667 --> 15:03.567
        Them too.               

15:03.569 --> 15:05.102
        [GIGGLING]              

