Oh, I'm telling you,            
it is so cold outside.          

17:28.247 --> 17:30.247
    It's a good thing           
        you bundled up.         

17:30.249 --> 17:32.449
That's right.                   
                Oh, yes.        

17:33.752 --> 17:34.852
                EDITH:          
                Look at you--   

17:34.854 --> 17:36.787
                you wore        
                your pajamas.   

17:36.789 --> 17:38.756
    Well, Trudy said,           
    "come as you are."          

17:38.758 --> 17:39.757
                         [GASPS]

17:39.759 --> 17:41.158
            Oh, my!             

17:41.160 --> 17:45.495
    Then this must be           
a "come as you are" party.      

17:45.497 --> 17:47.264
    [MUFFLED CHATTER]           

17:52.704 --> 17:54.004
                         Gloria!

17:54.006 --> 17:56.473
                Look who's here.

17:56.475 --> 17:59.577
Oh, Michael...                  

17:59.579 --> 18:01.111
        Hey...                  

18:01.113 --> 18:02.412
    Pizza!                      

18:06.718 --> 18:07.751
                         Oh!    

18:07.753 --> 18:10.988
        Oh, honey, I'm sorry.   

18:10.990 --> 18:12.923
            Oh, I'm sorry.      

18:12.925 --> 18:14.825
            How are you?        
            I missed you.       

18:14.827 --> 18:17.294
        I'm fine.               
  How did you know I was here?  

18:17.296 --> 18:19.863
Well, from out of nowhere,      
Archie asked Lionel about Trudy,

18:19.865 --> 18:21.331
 so I put two and two together. 

18:21.333 --> 18:22.700
Oh.                             

18:22.702 --> 18:27.204
        Uh, listen, I, uh,      
        I brought you something.

18:27.206 --> 18:28.472
    I wrote you a fresh poem.   

18:30.642 --> 18:33.310
Oh, Michael.                    

18:33.312 --> 18:34.612
                    Aw...       

18:34.614 --> 18:36.413
GLORIA: Oh, everybody,          
I want you to meet Michael.     

18:36.415 --> 18:37.881
He's my husband.                

18:37.883 --> 18:38.882
Michael,                        
you know Trudy.                 

18:38.884 --> 18:39.950
            Yeah.               
                        And you 
                        know me.

18:44.723 --> 18:46.256
And this is Betty Sue           
and Joanie.                     

18:46.258 --> 18:47.257
Michael.                        

18:47.259 --> 18:48.458
I'm gonna                       
read them the poem.             

18:48.460 --> 18:50.594
                     Oh, no, no.
[ALL PROTESTING]                

18:50.596 --> 18:53.430
                All right. It's 
                nothing, really.

18:53.432 --> 18:54.999
"Oh, Gloria,                    

18:55.001 --> 18:57.134
"You made                       
My life euphoria.               

18:57.136 --> 18:59.469
"I wanna                        
Get more of ya.                 

19:01.773 --> 19:04.574
Gloria, I adore ya."            

19:04.576 --> 19:07.044
Oh, Michael,                    
it's beautiful.                 

19:07.046 --> 19:08.646
Michael,                        
come here a minute.             

19:08.648 --> 19:11.048
I wanna talk to you.            

19:11.050 --> 19:15.619
I just wanna say I'm sorry.     
I was wrong.                    

19:15.621 --> 19:17.121
                I was wrong too.

19:17.123 --> 19:20.423
        I was wrong too.        

19:20.425 --> 19:23.027
      I should never have       
     walked out on Archie,      

19:23.029 --> 19:26.196
 and I'm gonna tell him too...  

19:26.198 --> 19:30.167
    if I ever see him again.    

19:30.169 --> 19:32.069
Aw, come on, Ma,                
cheer up.                       

19:32.071 --> 19:34.071
        All right.              

19:40.912 --> 19:42.780
                  Let's sing    
                  another song. 

19:42.782 --> 19:44.281
                        Yeah.   
            Yeah.               

19:44.283 --> 19:46.884
                 You all join in
                 on the chorus. 

19:46.886 --> 19:49.486
        ♪ A peanut sat          
    On the railroad track ♪     

19:49.488 --> 19:51.689
♪ His heart was all a-flutter ♪ 

19:51.691 --> 19:54.058
    ♪ Around the bend           
        Came the 8:15 ♪         

19:54.060 --> 19:56.493
♪ And now he's peanut butter ♪  

