20:07.506 --> 20:10.174
     ♪ It ain't gonna rain      
         No more... ♪           

20:10.176 --> 20:11.041
             Edith!             

20:12.543 --> 20:15.045
    You having a good time?     

20:15.047 --> 20:19.183
     Archie, you came back,     

20:19.185 --> 20:21.618
        just like in the movies!

20:30.328 --> 20:34.297
Take off                        
that Chinky bathrobe.           

