      No, Archie, we're having  
      a "come as you are" party.

20:36.969 --> 20:38.936
     Let me introduce you.      

20:38.938 --> 20:41.071
 You know Gloria, you know Mi-- 

20:41.073 --> 20:42.405
Cut that out.                   

20:44.142 --> 20:47.077
It's like                       
an opium joint in here.         

20:47.079 --> 20:48.678
Bunch of Commies                
doing hijinks.                  

20:48.680 --> 20:51.648
      Gloria, you didn't tell me
      you had a daddy like that.

20:51.650 --> 20:53.150
     What you mean by that?     

20:53.152 --> 20:55.619
Well, Mr. Bunker, my sister     
and I are from Dallas,          

20:55.621 --> 20:57.454
and our daddy would think       
you're a Communist.             

20:57.456 --> 20:58.521
ARCHIE: Why?                    

20:58.523 --> 20:59.790
Because you live                
in New York City.               

21:01.425 --> 21:03.794
Why don't you two sing him      
  your daddy's favorite song?   

21:03.796 --> 21:05.262
                 That's a       
                 terrific idea. 

21:05.264 --> 21:07.631
  Betty Sue, Joanie, come on.   

21:07.633 --> 21:09.032
                Don't be shy.   

21:09.034 --> 21:10.934
I don't want                    
to hear no song.                

21:10.936 --> 21:13.137
    Get away from me.           

