  ♪ For Democracy's the way ♪   

21:26.986 --> 21:29.619
♪ To live each and every day ♪  

21:29.621 --> 21:31.421
  ♪ So when Communism comes ♪   

21:31.423 --> 21:35.926
          ♪ Just say            
     You're not at home ♪       

21:35.928 --> 21:40.764
    ♪ From Democracy            
We'll never, ever roam ♪        

21:40.766 --> 21:41.631
                      [CHEERING]

21:48.106 --> 21:50.107
Well, your daddy's              
favorite song                   

21:50.109 --> 21:52.409
is a damn good song.            

21:52.411 --> 21:53.543
But I know very well            

21:53.545 --> 21:55.478
that youse two don't            
believe in it, see.             

21:55.480 --> 21:57.080
I know when my legs             
are being pulled                

21:57.082 --> 22:00.550
by a couple                     
o' little pinkos there.         

22:00.552 --> 22:02.786
And I think you ought           
to put some clothes on too.     

22:02.788 --> 22:04.788
I don't know why                
I'm looking at youse.           

22:07.725 --> 22:09.726
Come on. I think we ought       
to go home now.                 

22:09.728 --> 22:11.962
And that includes               
Gloria and Mike. Come on.       

22:11.964 --> 22:13.596
Oh, wait a minute,              
Archie.                         

22:13.598 --> 22:15.833
I want to tell you              
something.                      

22:15.835 --> 22:17.901
     I was wrong.               

22:17.903 --> 22:20.570
        Of course you was wrong.

22:22.073 --> 22:25.876
Well, don't you think you should
say you was wrong too?          

22:25.878 --> 22:27.744
              Wrong about what? 

22:27.746 --> 22:30.113
About Mike's privacy.           

22:30.115 --> 22:33.250
Everybody's got a right         
to their privacy.               

22:33.252 --> 22:35.685
        I got a right to know   
              whatever goes on  

22:35.687 --> 22:37.721
     with anybody under my roof!

22:37.723 --> 22:41.424
That's why we're not under      
      your roof right now.      

22:41.426 --> 22:43.793
Archie, couldn't you say        
you was wrong?                  

22:43.795 --> 22:45.195
I said I was wrong.             

22:45.197 --> 22:47.397
      I said I was wrong.       
      I said I was wrong.       

22:47.399 --> 22:50.567
Oh, well, in that case...       

22:50.569 --> 22:53.203
     youse were all wrong,      
          but I ain't.          

22:55.874 --> 22:58.108
Archie, we ain't coming home    

22:58.110 --> 23:01.678
until you say                   
we got a right to our privacy.  

23:01.680 --> 23:03.146
You know what that is, Edith?   

23:03.148 --> 23:05.883
 That is blackmail, blackmail-- 
    which is a worser crime     

23:05.885 --> 23:07.484
             than the crime     
        of searching his closet.

23:07.486 --> 23:09.552
        Oh! Oh, oh, oh!         

23:09.554 --> 23:11.188
                 So you admit   
                 you were wrong.
         Huh?                   

23:11.190 --> 23:12.389
                 You said you   
              committed a crime.

23:12.391 --> 23:13.423
     I never said anything.     

23:13.425 --> 23:14.958
                 You just said--
                 you just said  

23:14.960 --> 23:16.360
              that searching    
          my closet was a crime.

23:16.362 --> 23:17.560
      I never said nothing      
          about that.           

23:17.562 --> 23:19.062
Oh, Archie,                     
say you was wrong.              

23:19.064 --> 23:20.163
I was wrong.                    

23:20.165 --> 23:21.164
                    And I was   
                    wrong.      

23:21.166 --> 23:22.299
                And I was       
                wrong.          

23:22.301 --> 23:23.901
      What is this,             
     <i>True Confessions?</i>          

23:23.903 --> 23:26.236
    [MIMICKING] I was wrong.    
I was wrong. I was wrong.       

23:26.238 --> 23:27.371
He said it!                     

23:27.373 --> 23:28.872
     I never said nothing!      

23:28.874 --> 23:30.673
              ♪ For he's a jolly
                 Good fellow ♪  

23:30.675 --> 23:33.143
♪ For he's a jolly good         
