23:33.145 --> 23:35.212
     ♪ For he's a jolly good    
        Fellow... ♪             

23:35.214 --> 23:36.713
         Shut up!               

23:36.715 --> 23:40.217
♪ Which nobody                  
Can deny ♪                      

23:40.219 --> 23:41.618
♪ He said                       
He was wrong ♪                  

23:41.620 --> 23:44.154
                 Ah! Not that!  

23:44.156 --> 23:46.323
             [ARGUING]          

23:53.531 --> 23:56.900
Oh, Archie, here's a poem       
you wrote to me.                

23:56.902 --> 23:58.302
          I never wrote no poem.

23:58.304 --> 23:59.602
Oh, yeah, listen.               

23:59.604 --> 24:03.407
     "When skies are blue,      
        I think of you,         

24:03.409 --> 24:05.976
    and in the rain,            
        I think again."         

24:05.978 --> 24:07.744
            Oh, yeah, yeah.     

